item.tib: rdzogs pa chen po nges don thams cad 'dus pa / ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud / lta bsgom thams cad kyi snying po / rin po che rnam par bkod pa
rdzogs pa chen po ma rig mun pa sel bar byed pa'i lta ba ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud
rdzogs pa chen po lta ba thams cad kyi snying po'i rgyud ces bya ba
rdzogs pa chen po kun tu bzang po ye shes gsal bar ston pa'i rgyud ces bya ba
kun tu bzang po ye shes gsal bar ston pa'i rgyud phyi ma zhes bya ba
rdzogs pa chen po ye shes 'khor lo gsang ba mchog gi rgyud
'phags pa ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig gyis rgyud zhes bya ba

de bzhin gshegs pa thams kyi ting nge 'dzin yongs su bshad pa / ye shes 'dus pa'i mdo / theg pa chen po / gsang ba bla na med pa'i rgyud / chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa / gsang sngags gcig pa'i ye shes / rdzogs pa chen po'i don gsal bar byed pa'i rgyud / rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud
rig pa rang grol chen po thams cad 'grol ba'i rgyud
rin po che 'byung bar byed pa sgra thal 'gyur chen po'i rgyud zhes bya ba
rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi me long gi rgyud zhes bya ba
kun tu bzang po thugs kyi me long gi rgyud ces bya ba / thams cad ston pa'i rgyud
kun tu bzang po klong drug gi rgyud
